fields.description:
When using a properly formatted,non-existent volume ID with euca-delete-volume, there is no error returned.

{code}
# euca-delete-volume vol-D49B409C
[root@viking-01 ~]#
{code}

Based upon the behavior witnessed against AWS, we should return the error code InvalidVolume.NotFound.

{code}
$ ec2-delete-volume vol-98c716b9
Client.InvalidVolume.NotFound: The volume 'vol-98c716b9' does not exist.
{code}

*Reference*

* http://docs.aws.amazon.com/AWSEC2/latest/APIReference/api-error-codes.html ( reference InvalidVolume.NotFound )

